### Test Suite para API v1 (REST Client)
### Requiere la extensión "REST Client" en VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@apiKey = REEMPLAZAR_CON_CLAVE_SEGURA_32_BYTES

### 1. GET /clientes - incluye rut y datos financieros
GET {{baseUrl}}/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 1b. GET /clientes con filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/clientes?stage=WAITING_CUOTAS
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 2. GET /plan-pagos - retorna cliente, caso, contrato y cuotas
GET {{baseUrl}}/plan-pagos
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 3. GET /plan-pagos?solo_pendientes=true - retorna solo cuotas UNPAID y OVERDUE
GET {{baseUrl}}/plan-pagos?solo_pendientes=true
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 4. GET /cobranza - mantiene compatibilidad e incluye campos nuevos
GET {{baseUrl}}/cobranza
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 5. POST /pagos - con payment_event_id marca cuota como PAID
POST {{baseUrl}}/pagos
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caso_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "estado": "PAID",
  "monto": 100000,
  "payment_event_id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "fecha_pago": "2026-05-04T12:00:00Z",
  "monto_pagado": 100000
}

### 6. POST /pagos - con caso_id + numero_cuota marca cuota como PAID
POST {{baseUrl}}/pagos
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caso_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "estado": "PAID",
  "monto": 100000,
  "numero_cuota": 1,
  "fecha_pago": "2026-05-04T12:00:00Z",
  "monto_pagado": 100000
}

### 7. POST /pagos - con token inválido responde 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/pagos
Authorization: Bearer token_invalido_123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caso_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "estado": "PAID",
  "monto": 100000
}

### 8. GET /case-updates/:identifier - avances del caso por RUT
GET {{baseUrl}}/case-updates/16.798.821-0
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 8b. GET /case-updates/:identifier - con RUT inexistente
GET {{baseUrl}}/case-updates/99.999.999-K
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
